headerImgData = defaultHeaderImage;

// Show preview immediately

    const preview = document.getElementById("headerPreview");

    preview.style.display = "block";

// Keep upload functionality as backup
document.getElementById("headerUpload").addEventListener("change", function (event) {
    const file = event.target.files[0];
    if (file) {
        const reader = new FileReader();
        reader.onload = function (e) {
            headerImgData = e.target.result;
            const preview = document.getElementById("headerPreview");
            preview.src = headerImgData;
            preview.style.display = "block";
        };
        reader.readAsDataURL(file);
    }
});
function generateMOM() {
            // Get all form values
            const formData = {

                siteAddress: document.getElementById('siteAddress').value,
                reportingDate: formatDate(document.getElementById('reportingDate').value),

                specification: document.getElementById('specification').value,
                serialNo: document.getElementById('serialNo').value,
                yearOfMfg: document.getElementById('yearOfMfg').value,

                transformerMake: document.getElementById('transformerMake').value,
                problemIdentification: document.getElementById('problemIdentification').value,
                technicalInvestigation: document.getElementById('technicalInvestigation').value,
                rootCauseAnalysis: document.getElementById('rootCauseAnalysis').value,
                correctiveMaintenance: document.getElementById('correctiveMaintenance').value,
                systemRestoration: document.getElementById('systemRestoration').value,
                recommendedSpares: document.getElementById('recommendedSpares').value,

                customerPhone: document.getElementById('customerPhone').value,
                customerEmail: document.getElementById('customerEmail').value,
                engineerName: document.getElementById('engineerName').value,

            };

            // Generate PDF
            generatePDF(formData);

        async function generatePDF(data) {
            // Create a temporary div with the MOM content
            const tempDiv = document.createElement('div');
            tempDiv.innerHTML = generateMOMHTML(data);
            tempDiv.style.position = 'absolute';
            tempDiv.style.left = '-9999px';
            tempDiv.style.width = '190mm'; // A4 width minus margins
            tempDiv.style.minHeight = '277mm'; // A4 height minus margins
            tempDiv.style.backgroundColor = 'white';
            tempDiv.style.padding = '5mm';
            tempDiv.style.boxSizing = 'border-box';
            document.body.appendChild(tempDiv);

            try {
                // Convert HTML to canvas with higher scale
                const canvas = await html2canvas(tempDiv, {
                    scale: 2, // Higher scale for better quality
                    useCORS: true,
                    backgroundColor: '#ffffff',
                    width: tempDiv.offsetWidth,
                    height: tempDiv.offsetHeight,
                    allowTaint: true
                });

                // Create PDF
                const { jsPDF } = window.jspdf;
                const pdf = new jsPDF('p', 'mm', 'a4');
                
                const imgData = canvas.toDataURL('image/png', 1.0);
                
                // Use almost full A4 dimensions
                const imgWidth = 190; // Full width minus small margins
                const imgHeight = (canvas.height * imgWidth) / canvas.width;
                
                // Scale to fit full A4 page
                let finalHeight = imgHeight;
                if (imgHeight > 277) {
                    finalHeight = 277; // Full height minus margins
                }
                
                // Position at top-left with minimal margins
                pdf.addImage(imgData, 'PNG', 10, 10, imgWidth, finalHeight);

                // Download PDF
                pdf.save(`MOM_${data.customerName.replace(/\s+/g, '_')}_${data.reportingDate}.pdf`);
                
                alert('MOM PDF generated and downloaded successfully!');
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Error generating PDF:', error);
                alert('Error generating PDF. Please try again.');
            } finally {
                // Clean up
                document.body.removeChild(tempDiv);
            }
        }

        function formatDate(dateString) {
            if (!dateString) return '';
            const date = new Date(dateString);
            return date.toLocaleDateString('en-GB');
        }
